1
00:01:39,430 --> 00:01:43,330
[Road to Success]

2
00:01:44,750 --> 00:01:47,729
[Episode 32]

3
00:01:50,150 --> 00:01:50,840
I'm sorry.

4
00:01:51,479 --> 00:01:53,080
I can accept any punishment,

5
00:01:53,789 --> 00:01:55,920
and I can also withdraw from the match.

6
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:57,920
But I don't want my personal matters

7
00:01:58,350 --> 00:01:59,410
to affect Hengjiu.

8
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:07,080
Do you have any other questions?

9
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:12,400
About this, you can decide for yourselves.

10
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:17,000
Ms. Lin, Coach.

11
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,920
We want to take some time
to think it over.

12
00:02:19,920 --> 00:02:20,579
No problem.

13
00:02:21,630 --> 00:02:22,190
Let's go.

14
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,000
I'll take him out first.

15
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:27,630
Let me know when you've made a decision.

16
00:02:27,630 --> 00:02:28,870
-Okay.
-Okay.

17
00:02:30,610 --> 00:02:31,610
Let's go.

18
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,750
I don't get it.

19
00:02:43,750 --> 00:02:45,020
He's the one who did something wrong.

20
00:02:45,020 --> 00:02:46,450
What is there for us to consider?

21
00:02:46,450 --> 00:02:47,680
Wrong is wrong.

22
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,640
I know what you guys mean.

23
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:52,560
But I think we should
treat different things separately.

24
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:54,540
Besides, he's our opponent.

25
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:56,160
Don't act like a saint, okay?

26
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:58,690
He was shedding tears just now.

27
00:02:58,720 --> 00:03:00,450
Who knows if he was just acting?

28
00:03:00,460 --> 00:03:02,190
He just wanted us to forgive him

29
00:03:02,210 --> 00:03:03,940
and pretend nothing happened.

30
00:03:04,750 --> 00:03:05,910
If we report him,

31
00:03:06,430 --> 00:03:07,790
what will be the consequences?

32
00:03:07,790 --> 00:03:10,190
This could affect him
for the rest of his life.

33
00:03:10,190 --> 00:03:11,800
I think we should give him a chance.

34
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:13,120
If we give him a chance,

35
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:14,850
who's going to give us a chance?

36
00:03:15,750 --> 00:03:16,280
Fu,

37
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:17,590
if Hengjiu loses him,

38
00:03:17,590 --> 00:03:19,990
our chances of winning
will be much higher.

39
00:03:20,030 --> 00:03:20,590
Right.

40
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:25,420
Have you all forgotten what you said?

41
00:03:26,150 --> 00:03:28,560
We play football to win.

42
00:03:33,190 --> 00:03:33,840
Everyone,

43
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:36,120
do you remember what Director Qian said?

44
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:37,910
We are about
to take the college entrance exam.

45
00:03:37,910 --> 00:03:39,190
As long as we beat Hengjiu,

46
00:03:39,190 --> 00:03:41,520
we'll have a chance at special admission.

47
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:49,360
Qin,

48
00:03:50,190 --> 00:03:51,190
what do you think?

49
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:55,930
I don't know what to say.

50
00:03:57,670 --> 00:03:59,150
But if I had to say,

51
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,000
I think...

52
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:04,660
I still want to beat that Qin Qiechu
on the field.

53
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:07,010
He slapped us in the face,

54
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:08,810
so we have to hit back, right?

55
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:10,210
Come on.

56
00:04:10,870 --> 00:04:12,030
Is there something wrong with your brain?

57
00:04:12,030 --> 00:04:13,030
Are you talking to me?

58
00:04:13,030 --> 00:04:13,870
Isn't there?

59
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:15,870
This match is related to our future.

60
00:04:15,870 --> 00:04:16,600
If you don't want to go to college,

61
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:18,240
could you please not drag us down?

62
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,480
I drag you down?

63
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:20,390
I'll say it one last time.

64
00:04:20,390 --> 00:04:21,160
Listen carefully.

65
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:24,510
With your terrible grades,
do you even need me to drag you down?

66
00:04:24,510 --> 00:04:26,720
-Enough!
-Alright, alright!

67
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:28,800
You're desperate to go to college, huh?

68
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:29,710
Qin Ao.

69
00:04:29,830 --> 00:04:31,890
-Alright, alright.
-Don't touch me!

70
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,430
How about...

71
00:04:40,830 --> 00:04:42,720
we use Robert's Rules of Order?

72
00:04:43,430 --> 00:04:44,190
I agree.

73
00:04:44,830 --> 00:04:45,830
What do you think?

74
00:04:52,830 --> 00:04:53,510
Alright.

75
00:04:53,510 --> 00:04:54,640
Let's start voting.

76
00:05:00,550 --> 00:05:01,670
For those who think

77
00:05:02,190 --> 00:05:03,390
we should report him,

78
00:05:03,630 --> 00:05:04,690
stand on this side.

79
00:05:05,340 --> 00:05:06,560
For those who think we should let it go,

80
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,620
stand on this side.

81
00:05:26,380 --> 00:05:28,110
Do you want to sit down and wait?

82
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:41,010
Coach, Ms. Lin.

83
00:05:43,390 --> 00:05:45,190
-I…
-Have you made up your minds?

84
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:47,840
You guys talk.

85
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:48,870
Okay.

86
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,400
Come in with me.

87
00:06:13,870 --> 00:06:15,790
Is it true that no matter the outcome,

88
00:06:15,790 --> 00:06:16,790
you can accept it?

89
00:06:17,950 --> 00:06:19,610
Given the current situation,

90
00:06:19,930 --> 00:06:21,610
it's not really up to me, is it?

91
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,270
Yes.

92
00:06:42,420 --> 00:06:43,770
By a vote of 9 to 2,

93
00:06:44,190 --> 00:06:45,480
we decided not to report you

94
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:46,540
or call the police.

95
00:06:49,790 --> 00:06:50,880
You can go now.

96
00:06:53,080 --> 00:06:54,130
Why?

97
00:06:54,470 --> 00:06:55,310
Did you think

98
00:06:55,310 --> 00:06:57,110
we would definitely report you?

99
00:06:57,270 --> 00:06:58,000
I know.

100
00:06:58,310 --> 00:07:00,090
Even though
you didn't want us to report you,

101
00:07:00,090 --> 00:07:01,690
deep down,

102
00:07:01,950 --> 00:07:03,000
