106
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,360
We do want to win,

107
00:07:10,610 --> 00:07:12,540
but we want to beat you on the field.

108
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:13,590
Also,

109
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:16,120
that brat Qin Qiechu

110
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,820
has always been talking about us
behind our backs.

111
00:07:17,820 --> 00:07:20,080
We've wanted to crush him for a long time.

112
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:23,600
Just like that,
the special admission spots are gone.

113
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:25,530
So you guys better not go easy on us.

114
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,430
Or I'll regret it to death.

115
00:07:29,860 --> 00:07:31,620
Now do you know why?

116
00:07:34,159 --> 00:07:35,000
Thank you.

117
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,390
I'll give it my all.

118
00:07:44,890 --> 00:07:45,520
Right,

119
00:07:45,550 --> 00:07:47,390
