120
00:07:47,630 --> 00:07:49,120
This isn't a gift from me.

121
00:07:54,630 --> 00:07:56,620
[IOU] [Debtor: Fang Sulun]

122
00:07:58,830 --> 00:07:59,560
Keep it safe.

123
00:08:02,790 --> 00:08:03,590
Here.

124
00:08:03,990 --> 00:08:04,650
It's yours.

125
00:08:08,490 --> 00:08:09,420
Thank you,

126
00:08:09,620 --> 00:08:10,500
Lin Lu.

127
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:15,960
What's wrong?

128
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,480
I'm so proud.

129
00:08:19,950 --> 00:08:20,720
I know.

130
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:22,190
Me too.

131
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:25,360
They've really grown up.

132
00:08:28,050 --> 00:08:29,230
Then I'll...

133
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,510
