134
00:08:30,510 --> 00:08:33,240
-Of course we will.
-See you on the field.

135
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:34,370
See you on the field.

136
00:08:35,289 --> 00:08:37,520
Tell that brat Qin Qiechu

137
00:08:37,909 --> 00:08:39,270
