554
00:23:28,590 --> 00:23:32,030
[One Year Later]

555
00:23:30,410 --> 00:23:31,600
♪ Break through every haze of doubt ♪

556
00:23:32,340 --> 00:23:33,890
♪ Chase the light within me ♪

557
00:23:33,240 --> 00:23:34,370
We're almost there.

558
00:23:34,780 --> 00:23:37,300
[Sports Equipment Room]

559
00:23:34,830 --> 00:23:35,550
-Hello, Director.
-Hello, Director.

560
00:23:35,550 --> 00:23:36,270
Hello.

561
00:23:45,480 --> 00:23:46,880
Come and take a look.

562
00:23:47,650 --> 00:23:50,410
This is our sports equipment room.

563
00:23:52,920 --> 00:23:54,160
Here are the keys.

564
00:23:54,160 --> 00:23:54,750
Okay.

565
00:23:54,750 --> 00:23:55,750
This is your desk.

566
00:23:58,160 --> 00:23:59,020
Director Qian.

567
00:23:59,350 --> 00:24:01,550
I heard that the previous keeper

568
00:24:01,550 --> 00:24:04,200
was a woman who was the top student
at Yongchuan University.

569
00:24:04,200 --> 00:24:06,030
I heard during her tenure,

570
00:24:06,030 --> 00:24:07,070
not only did she lead our

571
00:24:07,070 --> 00:24:09,070
Hongjing Football Team
to the top of the league table,

572
00:24:09,070 --> 00:24:10,310
but now she's also applying for a Ph.D.

573
00:24:10,310 --> 00:24:11,400
That shows

574
00:24:11,720 --> 00:24:14,000
our sports equipment room

575
00:24:14,000 --> 00:24:15,480
is a lucky place.

576
00:24:17,070 --> 00:24:18,270
I wouldn't

577
00:24:18,270 --> 00:24:19,750
bring just anyone here.

578
00:24:21,200 --> 00:24:21,880
Okay, Director.

579
00:24:21,880 --> 00:24:23,480
I will definitely work hard.

580
00:24:24,350 --> 00:24:26,750
Alright, this is the rack for volleyballs.

581
00:24:27,000 --> 00:24:28,750
And this shelf is all shuttlecocks.

582
00:24:28,750 --> 00:24:29,950
Let's look over here.

583
00:24:31,070 --> 00:24:32,830
-This is...
-This is the equipment supply room.

584
00:24:32,830 --> 00:24:33,360
Alright?

585
00:24:55,930 --> 00:25:00,950
[Lucky Gifts]

586
00:24:56,460 --> 00:24:58,750
♪ Dreams made of dazzling starlight ♪

587
00:24:59,510 --> 00:25:01,770
♪ Light up the sky ♪

588
00:25:02,880 --> 00:25:04,620
♪ I run towards your world ♪

589
00:25:05,570 --> 00:25:08,500
♪ With a gaze that mirrors yours ♪

590
00:25:09,120 --> 00:25:16,830
[Lucky Gifts]

591
00:25:10,160 --> 00:25:12,340
♪ The rainbow deep within your heart ♪

592
00:25:13,310 --> 00:25:15,270
♪ Soaring atop the peak ♪

593
00:25:16,490 --> 00:25:18,480
♪ I'm right here by your side ♪

594
00:25:19,310 --> 00:25:22,730
♪ My heart beats in time with yours ♪

595
00:25:23,840 --> 00:25:25,860
♪ Through twists and daring adventures ♪

596
00:25:27,070 --> 00:25:28,740
♪ I'll help you embrace
your transformation ♪

597
00:25:29,590 --> 00:25:31,320
♪ And guard all that makes you
one of a kind ♪

598
00:25:31,240 --> 00:25:32,640
-He added a new one last time.
-Pass the ball!

599
00:25:32,640 --> 00:25:34,200
-Pass.
-What about mental health counseling now?

600
00:25:34,200 --> 00:25:35,350
We already have

601
00:25:35,350 --> 00:25:36,440
a professional
mental health support plan in place.

602
00:25:36,440 --> 00:25:36,720
Don't slack off.

603
00:25:36,720 --> 00:25:38,510
-And we've also brought in a team doctor.
-Pass the ball.

604
00:25:38,510 --> 00:25:39,880
-Quicken your feet!
-Don't worry.

605
00:25:39,880 --> 00:25:41,310
-Our training programs
-Pass.

606
00:25:41,310 --> 00:25:43,370
are tailored to the kids' condition.

607
00:25:43,480 --> 00:25:43,920
Pass the ball!

608
00:25:43,920 --> 00:25:46,160
-We've actually gone over budget.
-Come on, pump your arms!

609
00:25:46,160 --> 00:25:47,240
-Those in the back! Your arms!
-In fact, our training program

610
00:25:47,240 --> 00:25:48,480
-is not bad.
-Pass the ball!

611
00:25:48,480 --> 00:25:48,920
Is that so?

612
00:25:48,920 --> 00:25:50,580
Yes, it's actually very good.

613
00:25:51,030 --> 00:25:51,440
Okay.

614
00:25:51,460 --> 00:25:52,450
-Alright, let's leave it at that for now.
-Okay.

615
00:25:52,450 --> 00:25:53,440
I'll catch up with you later.

616
00:25:53,440 --> 00:25:53,770
Okay.

617
00:25:54,400 --> 00:25:55,310
He's finishing up soon.

618
00:25:55,310 --> 00:25:57,240
Do you want to wait for him in the lounge?

619
00:25:57,240 --> 00:25:58,880
No need. I'll watch him here.

620
00:25:58,900 --> 00:26:01,030
-Let me see who is slacking off.
-Okay.

621
00:26:01,480 --> 00:26:03,680
Why are you carrying so many materials?

622
00:26:04,070 --> 00:26:06,920
These are the upgraded plans
for the youth academy.

623
00:26:06,920 --> 00:26:09,440
He said that besides technique,

624
00:26:09,440 --> 00:26:11,570
mental health is also very important.

625
00:26:12,200 --> 00:26:12,800
Not bad.

626
00:26:13,350 --> 00:26:13,550
Pass the ball.

627
00:26:13,550 --> 00:26:14,950
That's very thoughtful.

628
00:26:15,920 --> 00:26:16,520
By the way,

629
00:26:16,590 --> 00:26:18,160
are you guys preparing

630
00:26:18,160 --> 00:26:19,720
a charity training camp in the mountains?

631
00:26:19,720 --> 00:26:21,650
Yes, I'm going the week after next.

632
00:26:21,720 --> 00:26:22,920
You know Wang Fa.

633
00:26:22,920 --> 00:26:25,310
He's continuing to offer free spots.

634
00:26:25,720 --> 00:26:26,830
He thinks no talent

635
00:26:26,830 --> 00:26:28,000
should be buried.

636
00:26:28,830 --> 00:26:30,640
The only problem is...

637
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:31,680
that...

638
00:26:32,070 --> 00:26:33,670
I'm under a little pressure.

639
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:35,310
The budget is too high,

640
00:26:35,310 --> 00:26:37,270
and the financial pressure is immense.

641
00:26:37,270 --> 00:26:38,590
No wonder.

642
00:26:38,590 --> 00:26:40,480
You look like you're going a little bald.

643
00:26:40,480 --> 00:26:41,550
Not at all!

644
00:26:41,550 --> 00:26:43,590
My hairline isn't receding at all.

645
00:26:43,920 --> 00:26:46,850
I'm telling you,
I've had thick hair since I was a kid.

646
00:26:47,400 --> 00:26:48,310
If you call this little hair,

647
00:26:48,310 --> 00:26:49,910
then what about bald people?

648
00:26:51,510 --> 00:26:52,830
Tian...

649
00:26:53,110 --> 00:26:54,640
still hasn't accepted you?

650
00:26:55,240 --> 00:26:56,240
Well...

651
00:26:57,550 --> 00:26:58,720
She said

652
00:26:58,720 --> 00:27:01,250
she'd only let me
take up her time after Wang Fa

653
00:27:01,640 --> 00:27:03,770
and I had run the training school well.

654
00:27:03,830 --> 00:27:04,720
Congratulations.

655
00:27:04,720 --> 00:27:06,980
That means she's finally coming around.

656
00:27:07,270 --> 00:27:08,550
Halfway there, I guess.

657
00:27:08,550 --> 00:27:09,550
But you're right.

658
00:27:10,030 --> 00:27:12,310
If I'm excellent enough, she'll see it.

659
00:27:12,880 --> 00:27:13,510
Right?

660
00:27:13,960 --> 00:27:16,790
I plan to, after everything is done,

661
00:27:17,350 --> 00:27:19,240
take a road trip to relax

662
00:27:19,240 --> 00:27:20,240
and clear my mind.

663
00:27:20,790 --> 00:27:21,720
You? Driving?

664
00:27:22,000 --> 00:27:24,440
Are you sure you won't get lost
once on the road?

665
00:27:24,440 --> 00:27:25,640
-I…
-Don't worry.

666
00:27:27,440 --> 00:27:30,500
I had someone
make a special navigation system for you.

667
00:27:32,230 --> 00:27:33,190
What do you mean?

668
00:27:34,720 --> 00:27:35,450
Just in time.

669
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:36,540
Mr. Principal,

670
00:27:36,640 --> 00:27:37,480
please work overtime

671
00:27:37,480 --> 00:27:38,940
and finalize these plans.

672
00:27:39,030 --> 00:27:39,960
I can't do it today.

673
00:27:39,960 --> 00:27:41,000
I'll do it tomorrow morning.

674
00:27:41,000 --> 00:27:41,530
Let's go.

675
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:42,680
Tomorrow?

676
00:27:42,680 --> 00:27:43,170
Wait.

677
00:27:43,790 --> 00:27:45,160
Tomorrow is Saturday!

678
00:27:45,720 --> 00:27:46,720
You are exploiting your employee!

679
00:27:46,720 --> 00:27:47,440
Tell me.

680
00:27:47,920 --> 00:27:50,380
What trick did you pull
with his navigation?

681
00:27:51,200 --> 00:27:53,530
I did some special processing to the voice

682
00:27:54,790 --> 00:27:56,920
and changed it into Wang Tian's voice.

683
00:27:57,030 --> 00:27:58,480
With my sister's sarcasm,

684
00:27:58,480 --> 00:28:00,540
he definitely won't get lost easily.

685
00:28:00,880 --> 00:28:02,540
Use one evil to fight another?

686
00:28:03,780 --> 00:28:05,390
Good idea.

687
00:28:14,790 --> 00:28:16,320
Want to go in and have a look?

688
00:28:16,830 --> 00:28:18,290
Maybe there's a surprise.

689
00:28:36,590 --> 00:28:37,240
Is this...

690
00:28:43,500 --> 00:28:47,250
[Happy Birthday]

691
00:28:44,550 --> 00:28:47,010
Is this the surprise
you were talking about?

692
00:28:51,400 --> 00:28:52,900
[Ms. Lin, Happy birthday]

693
00:28:53,590 --> 00:28:55,160
Surprise!

694
00:28:55,480 --> 00:28:57,080
You startled me.

695
00:28:57,480 --> 00:28:58,510
What brings you here?

696
00:28:58,510 --> 00:29:00,110
To celebrate your birthday.

697
00:29:00,920 --> 00:29:02,320
Did you prepare all this?

698
00:29:04,310 --> 00:29:05,030
Thank you.

699
00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:07,270
Ms. Lin, happy birthday!

700
00:29:07,880 --> 00:29:10,880
We wish you a successful return
to Yongchuan

701
00:29:10,880 --> 00:29:13,440
and hope you
take back everything you lost!

702
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:15,590
Thank you.

703
00:29:15,590 --> 00:29:18,120
But am I some female version
of Edmond Dantès?

704
00:29:18,160 --> 00:29:19,510
Just kidding.

705
00:29:19,510 --> 00:29:21,000
I grilled all these just now.

706
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:21,550
I have more ingredients over there.

707
00:29:21,550 --> 00:29:22,880
I'll go grill some more.

708
00:29:23,000 --> 00:29:24,550
Coach, here. Have some milk.

709
00:29:24,550 --> 00:29:25,270
Where is Chen Jianghe?

710
00:29:25,270 --> 00:29:26,880
Didn't you say he was coming with you?

711
00:29:26,880 --> 00:29:28,570
Don't mention him.

712
00:29:28,920 --> 00:29:30,240
He booked the high-speed rail ticket

713
00:29:30,240 --> 00:29:31,640
but was temporarily dragged away
by his teacher.

714
00:29:31,640 --> 00:29:32,310
He had no choice.

715
00:29:32,310 --> 00:29:33,550
The sports university
suddenly had an event,

716
00:29:33,550 --> 00:29:34,270
and they were short on staff.

717
00:29:34,270 --> 00:29:35,550
The whole student union had to go.

718
00:29:35,550 --> 00:29:36,200
But

719
00:29:36,200 --> 00:29:37,550
he told me to wish you

720
00:29:37,550 --> 00:29:38,790
a happy birthday.

721
00:29:39,160 --> 00:29:40,720
I should thank him too.

722
00:29:40,720 --> 00:29:41,520
I understand.

723
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:44,550
These kids are so outstanding now.

724
00:29:44,450 --> 00:29:47,460
[Ms. Lin, Happy birthday]

725
00:29:44,550 --> 00:29:46,030
Why don't you bribe them

726
00:29:46,030 --> 00:29:48,000
and recruit them to work at your school?

727
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:49,160
That's a good idea.

728
00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:49,790
No, no.

729
00:29:50,270 --> 00:29:51,220
No need to bribe us at all.

730
00:29:51,220 --> 00:29:52,550
We'd be happy to do that.

731
00:29:52,550 --> 00:29:54,270
Right,
although they aren't here in person,

732
00:29:54,270 --> 00:29:55,790
all their gifts are here.

733
00:29:55,890 --> 00:29:57,850
[Happy Birthday]

734
00:29:56,480 --> 00:29:57,960
This one is from Zhi Hui.

735
00:29:57,960 --> 00:30:00,160
And Yu Ming, Zheng Ren, Jiang...

736
00:30:00,590 --> 00:30:01,520
Right, this one.

737
00:30:01,640 --> 00:30:03,030
This is the most important one.

738
00:30:03,030 --> 00:30:04,720
We wrote this ourselves.

739
00:30:07,840 --> 00:30:08,370
[Ms. Lin: May you live a long and happy life,
stay 18 forever, shine with endless beauty,]

740
00:30:08,350 --> 00:30:09,920
So many idioms?

741
00:30:08,390 --> 00:30:08,920
[be dazzling in every way, enjoy
lasting health and happiness, smile like a flower,]

742
00:30:08,940 --> 00:30:09,110
[stay full of energy,
and have a very happy birthday!]

743
00:30:09,110 --> 00:30:09,510
[By the handsome guys
from Hongjing No. 8 High School]

744
00:30:10,160 --> 00:30:11,200
That's very thoughtful of you.

745
00:30:11,200 --> 00:30:11,800
Thank you.

746
00:30:12,720 --> 00:30:13,920
The beef is here.

747
00:30:13,060 --> 00:30:21,080
[Happy Birthday]

748
00:30:14,590 --> 00:30:15,590
Ms. Lin,

749
00:30:15,590 --> 00:30:16,720
let me tell you, this beef

750
00:30:16,720 --> 00:30:17,680
is very special.

751
00:30:18,070 --> 00:30:20,070
Zheng Feiyang
had it flown in from Shandong.

752
00:30:20,070 --> 00:30:21,510
It's beef from
southwestern Shandong yellow cattle.

753
00:30:21,510 --> 00:30:22,160
It's super tender.

754
00:30:22,160 --> 00:30:23,490
A birthday gift for you.

755
00:30:24,070 --> 00:30:25,400
Tell him thank you.

756
00:30:25,400 --> 00:30:26,660
What is he up to lately?

757
00:30:27,160 --> 00:30:28,960
That kid is doing great.

758
00:30:28,960 --> 00:30:30,960
Whenever he has no classes,
he goes shop-hopping as a vlogger.

759
00:30:30,960 --> 00:30:32,360
He has a ton of followers.

760
00:30:33,890 --> 00:30:39,550
[Happy Birthday]

761
00:30:33,960 --> 00:30:34,960
A vlogger?

762
00:30:34,960 --> 00:30:37,690
Then I have to take a picture of him
for my content.

763
00:30:38,680 --> 00:30:39,920
Sorry I'm late.

764
00:30:41,640 --> 00:30:44,000
Wen Chengye? Aren't you in the US?

765
00:30:44,270 --> 00:30:45,070
Spring break.

766
00:30:47,680 --> 00:30:48,540
Thank you

767
00:30:48,640 --> 00:30:51,970
-To celebrate my birthday, you came...
-You think too much.

768
00:30:52,350 --> 00:30:55,210
I was planning to come back
for spring break anyway.

769
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:58,510
You haven't changed a bit.

770
00:30:58,510 --> 00:30:59,480
Indeed.

771
00:30:59,750 --> 00:31:02,750
The ugly face of a capitalist.

772
00:31:03,200 --> 00:31:03,960
I just came back,

773
00:31:03,960 --> 00:31:04,960
-and you have started...
-What?

774
00:31:04,960 --> 00:31:06,030
What about it?

775
00:31:06,030 --> 00:31:08,750
Captain, how does
your first year of college feel?

776
00:31:08,750 --> 00:31:09,510
Not bad.

777
00:31:09,510 --> 00:31:11,480
There's not much pressure
at Hongjing Normal University anyway.

778
00:31:11,480 --> 00:31:13,400
We'll see when we start job hunting
after graduation.

779
00:31:13,400 --> 00:31:14,930
Ms. Lin, Coach, have a seat.

780
00:31:15,070 --> 00:31:15,730
Have a seat.

781
00:31:26,030 --> 00:31:26,640
Lu.

782
00:31:26,920 --> 00:31:27,640
Lu?

783
00:31:28,920 --> 00:31:29,590
Boss! Boss!

784
00:31:29,590 --> 00:31:30,790
Have you seen Ms. Lin?

785
00:31:31,800 --> 00:31:33,760
-Lu, long time no see.
-Ms. Lin!

786
00:31:33,030 --> 00:31:36,340
[Skipping Work to Celebrate a Birthday.
Unfollow Me If You Must]

787
00:31:33,790 --> 00:31:35,270
I miss you so much!

788
00:31:35,270 --> 00:31:36,590
Happy birthday!

789
00:31:36,590 --> 00:31:37,880
Thank you.

790
00:31:37,880 --> 00:31:39,200
What does the title

791
00:31:38,880 --> 00:31:40,890
[Skipping Work to Celebrate a Birthday.
Unfollow Me If You Must]

792
00:31:39,200 --> 00:31:40,600
of your livestream mean?

793
00:31:41,440 --> 00:31:43,480
Skipping work to celebrate a birthday.

794
00:31:43,480 --> 00:31:45,050
Unfollow me if you must?

795
00:31:45,350 --> 00:31:46,110
Keep a low profile.

796
00:31:45,400 --> 00:31:49,980
[Skipping Work to Celebrate a Birthday.
Unfollow Me If You Must]

797
00:31:46,110 --> 00:31:48,880
I haven't reached my streaming hours
this month.

798
00:31:48,900 --> 00:31:51,300
Let me just stay live
and rack up some hours.

799
00:31:51,350 --> 00:31:52,950
Do you need me to play for you?

800
00:31:53,480 --> 00:31:55,510
Ms. Lin, your skills are too good.

801
00:31:55,530 --> 00:31:57,800
Everyone in my stream knows I suck.

802
00:31:56,690 --> 00:31:59,310
[Skipping Work to Celebrate a Birthday.
Unfollow Me If You Must]

803
00:31:58,030 --> 00:31:59,630
They'd expose me in a second.

804
00:32:00,200 --> 00:32:02,680
Ms. Lin,
are you and Coach doing well lately?

805
00:32:03,070 --> 00:32:05,110
I'll definitely visit you
once I'm done with work.

806
00:32:05,110 --> 00:32:05,680
Okay.

807
00:32:07,920 --> 00:32:09,380
Is this delicious, Coach?

808
00:32:10,590 --> 00:32:11,350
Yes.

809
00:32:11,510 --> 00:32:12,830
Zheng Feiyang sent it.

810
00:32:13,240 --> 00:32:14,690
Let's play together when you come back.

811
00:32:14,360 --> 00:32:17,130
[Skipping Work to Celebrate a Birthday.
Unfollow Me If You Must]

812
00:32:14,960 --> 00:32:15,890
Please carry me!

813
00:32:17,240 --> 00:32:17,960
By the way, Boss.

814
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:18,960
What is it?

815
00:32:19,110 --> 00:32:22,240
This new gaming chair I bought
is super comfortable.

816
00:32:22,270 --> 00:32:23,650
[Fun-to-Watch Streamer] [Peak King Lu]

817
00:32:22,350 --> 00:32:24,110
You must try it when you're here.

818
00:32:24,110 --> 00:32:24,880
Okay.

819
00:32:25,550 --> 00:32:26,160
Hello.

820
00:32:26,160 --> 00:32:27,640
Can I try it out?

821
00:32:27,640 --> 00:32:29,100
Okay, okay. No problem!

822
00:32:29,350 --> 00:32:30,590
Alright, that's enough.

823
00:32:30,590 --> 00:32:32,640
I'll add everyone to a group chat later.

824
00:32:32,640 --> 00:32:34,510
Just join it,

825
00:32:34,510 --> 00:32:36,550
and then we can hop on a call together.

826
